header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - 2ND ROUND

videos.description: Keyshawn Woods finds John Collins who finishes with the strong jam for Wake Forest.
videos.headline: Wake Forest starts on a 12-4 run with dunk by Collins

videos.description: Zach LeDay tries to get the tip shot but Wake Forest's Konstantinos Mitoglou flies high for the rejection.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's Mitoglou comes out of nowhere for the block

videos.description: Greg McClinton goes with the football toss and makes the bucket just like he drew it up for Wake Forest at the first-half buzzer.
videos.headline: Wake Forest's McClinton hits buzzer-beater from opposite free throw line

videos.description: Danny Manning talks about the shot before the buzzer and his teams offense.
videos.headline: Wake Forest coach Danny Manning talks about his teams first half offense

videos.description: Seth Allen misses his first opportunity but gets another one and drains a 3-pointer for Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Second time is the charm for Virginia Tech's Allen

videos.description: Justin Robinson splits two defenders and gives the assist to Zach LeDay for the dunk.
videos.headline: Nice dime leads to wide open dunk for Virginia Tech's LeDay

videos.description: Zach LeDay explains what this win means to his team and about his amazing night on the court.
videos.headline: Virginia Tech's Zach LeDay talks about his career night
